{"tid":785324,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩遊戲勾起你童年回憶。","createTime":"2018-08-19T06:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T06:34:51.000Z","uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d04fc8a22b1adc195c6c995268eb474cec62b46","tid":785324,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"以前玩完一隻遊戲通完關就會去玩另一隻遊戲，無咩特別感覺，但人大咗聽番啲遊戲音樂就覺得自己好似失去咗啲咩咁。以前小學初中從來只會考試前讀書，仲要不甘情願拎起本書，等家人出街就拎部Nds偷玩。家陣長大了已再沒閒情逸致玩⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n以前最鍾意玩既除咗跑Online，仲有Nds既遊戲（仲要多謝R4晶片），例如寵物小精靈dp pt hg/ss bw1,2，諗番起先覺得正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，勾起晒我的童年回憶，家陣遊戲畫面再靚都比唔上舊時遊戲咁好玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/142639_cfb052889c445bd518e465593174534a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F142639_cfb052889c445bd518e465593174534a.gif&h=1a9a5439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rd83jMTERqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Drd83jMTERqM&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c5bd8db9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rd83jMTERqM</a>"},{"pid":"0d133aad141ddff45606995350f2e232735093b2","tid":785324,"uid":45473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"洛克人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8491a3e831bb96351013d1ff575b37ff51e7de0","tid":785324,"uid":14130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d133aad141ddff45606995350f2e232735093b2","tid":785324,"uid":45473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"洛克人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"GB X同X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}